summary: Hello! Do you have a favorite pokemon?  Wishing you and your family a prosperous 2019!!
question: Hello! Do you have a favorite pokemon?  Wishing you and your family a prosperous 2019!!
answer:
Thank you so much, and the same to you!

As for a favorite Pokémon…I can’t say I really have one. I’m not a gamer, and when I kinda was, I played sports and and sim and FPS games, so I’ve pretty much missed all the Pokémon games. My experience with the franchise has been through anime and even with that it’s been tempered because I’m a Digimon fan. :)

tags: like im selling A LOT of my stuff bc bby i got no space at the new place ;;
summary: I work a close tonight then tomorrow I'm off for 4 days but that means I'm gonna be going threw every little thing I own and...
body:
I work a close tonight then tomorrow I’m off for 4 days but that means I’m gonna be going threw every little thing I own and debating if it will fit in the studio apartment that we are going to get, like the goal is to have everything ready for our move out/in date (3/1) and its gonna be some difficult

But like goal is to get rid of stuff by 2/20 so tomorrow I’m gonna be putting my stuff that wont fit in the new place on my mercari which y'all should watch! But after the 25th of Feb I’m gonna donate a lot of it ;; https://www.mercari.com/u/252290312 ( And if you dont already have an account use my code QNTEQR to signup >w> )

(I have a lot of vintage, collectibles, pokemon, neopets, toys, manga, comic heroes, ect that’s the kinda thing I’ll be selling so if that sounds up your alley feel free to look bc I’ll have new stuff going up till Wednesday.)

All the money I get will be going to pet deposits fees, new appartment fees and also paying off my $2,400 dollar debt :’) so hmu!
